OL,3,CWoman in her 20s in critical condition
OL,4,Cafter stabbing in Oldham
OL,6,FA woman in her 20s is in critical
OL,7,Fcondition in hospital after a stabbing
OL,8,Fin Oldham.
OL,10,FPolice attended a property on
OL,11,FGreenwood Street at around 10:40pm on
OL,12,FFriday 27 March after reports of an
OL,13,Fassault.
OL,15,FOfficers found the woman with serious
OL,16,Finjuries.
OL,18,FNo arrests have been made.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
