OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774872666
OL,3,CWoman in her 20s in critical condition
OL,4,Cafter stabbing in Oldham
OL,6,FChief Inspector Ian Partington from
OL,7,FGreater Manchester Police said: "This
OL,8,Fwas a shocking incident of violence,
OL,9,Fand our thoughts remain with the
OL,10,Fvictim at this incredibly difficult
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,F"I would like to reassure the
OL,14,Fcommunity that incidents of this
OL,15,Fnature are taken extremely seriously
OL,16,Fand our officers are currently
OL,17,Fexhausting all lines of enquiry to
OL,18,Flocate the suspect.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
