OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774872666
OL,3,CWoman in her 20s in critical condition
OL,4,Cafter stabbing in Oldham
OL,6,F"We understand this is a concerning
OL,7,Fincident, and we have extra patrols in
OL,8,Fthe area following this incident. I
OL,9,Fencourage anyone with concerns to
OL,10,Fplease speak with our officers who are
OL,11,Fthere to support.
OL,13,F"A scene remains in place and our
OL,14,Fofficers have worked through the night
OL,15,Fto conduct their investigation.
OL,17,F"I urge anyone who may have witnessed
OL,18,Fthis incident or has dashcam, CCTV or
OL,19,Fmobile phone from the area at the time
OL,20,Fto please report to us."
